description.p:
In a further form, a method of producing a mask is disclosed, the method including the steps of:
moulding two contoured recesses in one or more padding parts to form part of a body, the contoured recesses being associated with eyes of a wearer;
locating the one or more padding parts between an outer portion and a face portion;
connecting the outer portion to the face portion; and
connecting a retaining part to the body.
